CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 7, 1961, pg. 15, reads: "Beautiful Yard Awards to 243 Families - Majestic Lawn - in Mulford St. area, at 7604, is the majestic lawn of Mr. and Mrs. Charles (Teenie) Harris, which is a sight of beauty the year 'round."
TitMainTitle: Backyard of Charles "Teenie" Harris' house with birdbath, and chain link fence in foreground, 7604 Mulford Street, Homewood
